Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.11,1:38:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,moves on from there to there. So the\Nunfolding of the hand is the opening of
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.71,1:38:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a potentiality.\NThink of it more like emerges. Think it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.36,1:38:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like a like a crystis and the and and\Nthe pupa there emerges. It has the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.36,1:38:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality becoming a butterfly, but\Nnothing is causing anything. It can only
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.63,1:38:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfill its potentiality when local\Nconditions are favorable. If they're not
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.76,1:38:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,favorable, it will collapse. And\Nkarmically was never destined to man to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.71,1:38:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,manifest.\NUh it's a more of a meditative thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.04,1:38:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're contemplative. You're walking\Naround, you begin to notice that
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.60,1:38:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is happening of its own.\NNothing is causing anything at all in
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.84,1:39:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the universe. That's a limiting concept.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.76,1:39:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> In our society, it's hard to transcend\Nbecause of science and you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.67,1:39:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,accountability and all such you know.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.88,1:39:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> But you can get beyond it.\N>> Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.44,1:39:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> If you you know why? Why? Why can you\Nget beyond it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.67,1:39:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Prayer and intention.\N>> Because that's your potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.63,1:39:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If your intention is to transcend it,\Nthen you're obviously going to transcend
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.56,1:39:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it.\N>> Or you wouldn't be asking the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.63,1:39:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's guaranteed that he's going to\Ntranscend causality. Everybody in favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.97,1:39:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> [applause]\N>> He's going to do it for all of us.
